Mvh

The info how to crack this is minimal, minimal in that sence it's missing all together. 

Heres how to do it. 

1. start Install (from disc or mount image) 
2. run keygen to get a serial and enter it in. 

after setup is complete you must activate the program. 
3. disconnect your internet (pull the plug or disable network) 
4. choose "activate but not register". 
5. program tryes to connect to norton server a few times. 
6. a new option to activate is displayed. choose "phone". 
7. run keygen again and type in the activation code (in one line works, don't have to have - between). 
8. generate activation code and enter in norton (copy n paste works on all numbers in one stroke). 

norton is registerd. turn on your internet and update the program to the latest version and protection.
